<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #0056b3;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .benefits {
      background: #e9ecef;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Syrnyk, {{firstName}}!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Thank you for joining our community! We're delighted to have you as our customer.</p>
      
      <div class="benefits">
        <h3>Your benefits as a registered customer:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Easily track your orders</li>
          <li>Save delivery preferences</li>
          <li>Get access to exclusive offers</li>
          <li>Fast checkout process</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>Now you can log into your account to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>View order history</li>
        <li>Update profile information</li>
        <li>Manage delivery addresses</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>Your Syrnyk Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>